      .event-container
        p.event Prayers and Fasting - Thursday 25th<br> All Day
        .event-details Join us for our Prayers and Fasting event — a dedicated time to seek God’s presence, strengthen our faith, and grow in spiritual discipline. Through prayer, reflection, and fasting, we humble ourselves before God, inviting His guidance, healing, and renewal in our lives. This is a sacred opportunity to deepen your relationship with Him and align your heart with His will. Everyone is encouraged to participate as we unite in faith and devotion. We also have communion at 19:00.

